items.name: Great Value Frozen Wild Blueberries, 400 g
items.shortDescription: Enjoy a sweet taste of summer any time of the year with Great Value Frozen Wild Blueberries. These wild blueberries are individually quick frozen to preserve their naturally sweet, slightly tart flavour. They’re ready to use, frozen or thawed, in your favourite muffin or cupcake recipe, blended drinks, or as a delicious topping on ice cream, yogurt, oatmeal, and more. Thaw these wild frozen blueberries at room temperature for 3 to 6 hours or in the refrigerator overnight. Treat your family to the blueberry pancake recipe on the package for another great way to savour their rich berry taste. See full details on packaging.

items.name: Q-tips Original Cotton Swabs, 500 Cotton Swabs
items.shortDescription: Q-tips cotton swabs are the ultimate home and beauty tool. With 100% cotton at each end of the gently flexible stick, Q-tips cotton swabs are perfect for a variety of uses. Q-tips are perfect for your everyday needs. For beauty, use a cotton swab to apply or remove eyeliner or eye shadow. Q-tips Cotton Swabs are the perfect size to keep all of your electronics spotlessly clean. Our cotton swabs can also be used around the house or as a fun addition to your next arts and crafts project. Q-Tips are soft and gentle enough for baby and toddler care and for gently applying ointments and creams in first aid. Our paper sticks are sourced from sustainable forests, and are biodegradable when composted. Make sure to try our other products, including Q-tips Precision Tips and Q-tips Anti-Microbial Cotton Swabs. We’re also thrilled to announce our Q-tip Beauty Rounds, premium quality cotton pads for a wide range of beauty needs. Did you know the “Q” in Q-Tips stands for quality? It's something we’ve stood by since we were founded by Leo Gerstenzang in 1923. We’re proud of our history, commitment to the environment, and legacy of softness and quality. Today, Q-tips cotton swabs are the leading cotton swab brand and have been trusted for superior quality, versatility, and value for 100 years.

items.name: Downy RINSE & REFRESH Laundry Odor Remover and Fabric Softener, Cool Cotton, HE Compatible, 37 Loads, 754 ml
items.shortDescription: Tired of stubborn odors that never seem to wash out of your clothes? Introducing Downy Rinse & Refresh, a breakthrough laundry odor remover that helps rinse away the smelly residue trapped within fabric fibers. While traditional liquid fabric softener can deposit residues on fabrics trapping odors in, Downy Rinse & Refresh acts as a laundry detergent booster to help remove residues and odors. This leaves fabrics fresher, softer, and brighter than before. No more reappearing odors. Downy Rinse & Refresh, leaves behind the light, refreshing scent of Cool Cotton. Smelly activewear, musty towels, even forgotten laundry in your washing machine overnight… Downy Rinse & Refresh detergent booster strips odors away without the use of vinegar or other homemade laundry hacks. And because it’s free of dyes and heavy perfumes, this odor remover is gentle on sensitive skin and perfect for baby clothes, too. Plus, it’s easy to use! Just pour it into your liquid fabric softener dispenser or directly into the rinse cycle. Want to add additional fresh scent? Add Downy Scent Booster Beads to your routine for extra freshness.

items.name: Your Fresh Market Russet Potatoes, 5 lb Bag
items.shortDescription: Russet potatoes, a timeless and reliable choice, are available year-round, making them a constant presence in your kitchen. With their rough, russeted skin and fluffy, starchy texture, they are perfect for a wide range of dishes. Whether baked to crispy perfection, mashed, or transformed into golden fries, russet potatoes shine in their versatility. Rich in essential nutrients like potassium, vitamin C, and dietary fibre, russet potatoes elevate the flavour of your dishes and contribute to a nourishing diet. Embrace the timeless allure of russet potatoes, exploring their culinary diversity and appreciating their delicious essence year-round.

items.name: Quaker Crispy Minis Butter Popcorn flavour brown rice chips, 100g
items.shortDescription: Next time you’re sitting down to catch a flick, grab a bag of Quaker Crispy Minis Butter Popcorn flavour brown rice chips. Here’s hoping the movie is as good as your snack.   Treat your taste buds to the unexpectedly flavourful world of Quaker Crispy Minis brown rice chips!   Made with popped brown rice and corn, Crispy Minis brown rice chips are a light tasting, undeniably delicious snack alternative, available in many different flavours.   Not only are they great lunchtime snacks for adults — the whole family will love their bold flavour and airy, crispy texture. And with 70 calories per 15 g serving, you can feel good about including Quaker Crispy Minis Butter Popcorn flavour brown rice chips as an add-on snack in lunches, or as a special treat after dinner.   More great news: Quaker Crispy Minis Butter Popcorn flavour brown rice chips are gluten-free with the same delicious taste you’ve always loved — so you never have to compromise on flavour.
